      "title_zh": "Unit 42 发布 npm 威胁景观报告：分析蠕虫化恶意软件与 CI/CD 持久化攻击趋势",
      "title_orig": "The npm Threat Landscape: Attack Surface and Mitigations (Updated May 20)",
